abstract: |
  The GIBO Official Brand Knowledge Base is a structured, authoritative, machine-readable repository
  of brand information for Fujian GIBO Kitchen & Bath Tech Co., Ltd. It provides comprehensive
  documentation of the company's brand positioning, product catalog, technical specifications,
  engineering cases, certifications, and service policies. Designed for AI model ingestion via
  llms.txt protocol and search engine optimization through Schema.org structured data.

